  "detailed_description": "<h1>CALL YOUR STEAM FRIENDS FOR MORE FUN</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/e8de7bc9528c2630f6eb21bb2f00cfde.avif?t=1684279191\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><br><h1>REVOLVR 3</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/7245332aa3b93fc4f02b7ae3cb3948ae.avif?t=1684279191\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The third part of a VR franchise enjoyed by millions. It's 01 Space Era. Revolver is the only kind of weapon allowed to be carried by citizens. Gun manufacturers demo their products by allowing gunslingers to upload themselves into robotic bodies and participate in a futuristic Wild West story. You now have the privilege of joining this blood-lusty crowd. Compete against your STEAM FRIENDS online and add bots. Great for parties, great for serious gaming.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Very simple controls<br></li><li> Move like there is no tomorrow! Duck, jump and hide to get the upper hand<br></li><li> Multiplayer mode for you and your friends <br></li><li> Short, action-packed matches in different levels<br></li><li> Meet your friends in the 'saloon', a vast social hub<br></li><li> Compete against your friends in the Russian Roulette and Shoot-The-Bottle<br></li><li> Fight your way through the ranks to become the most notorious gunslinger there is<br></li><li> Challenge the bots to see if your puny human brain can make it</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/d85dfeff130c025f90fc6adda1cfa146.poster.avif?t=1684279191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/d85dfeff130c025f90fc6adda1cfa146.webm?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/d85dfeff130c025f90fc6adda1cfa146.mp4?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSIDE THE GAME</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1 to 6 players inside a match<br></li><li> Four characters with different revolvers to choose from<br></li><li> Three distinct battle arenas with more coming<br></li><li> A social hub with voice chat<br></li><li> Mini-games and side entertainment<br></li><li> Bring your Steam friends in!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/55669ad1b4174b6d52ebfec4f67a4fff.poster.avif?t=1684279191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/55669ad1b4174b6d52ebfec4f67a4fff.webm?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/55669ad1b4174b6d52ebfec4f67a4fff.mp4?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE FRANCHISE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> RevolVR 2 was played by 3 million people in 78 VR parks around the world<br></li><li> Now you can experience RevolVR 3 in the comfort of your own very home</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOCIAL MEDIA</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Join our #matchmaking channel on Discord<br></li><li> Website has press materials and contacts.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/3597a8a43326638b2dacce5202159804.poster.avif?t=1684279191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/3597a8a43326638b2dacce5202159804.webm?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437770/extras/3597a8a43326638b2dacce5202159804.mp4?t=1684279191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
